            <h2>How Do I Get To and From Terminal 4? </h2>
            <p>Getting to and from T4 is simple thanks to PHX Sky Harbour's transport options, and you can choose the PHX Sky Train because this is a free and automated train, which is the best friend at Sky Harbor. It directly connects Terminal 4 to Terminal 3, the Rental Car Centre, the East Economy Parking lot, and the 44th Street/Washington Valley Metro Rail Station. If you're connecting between Terminal 4 and Terminal 3, just hop on the Sky Train on Level 3 of T4. </p>
            <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>
